entry.tran: 不典型的；不代表…的特征的；反常的
entry.def: If you describe something as uncharacteristic of someone, you mean that it is not typical of them.

example.ex: It was uncharacteristic of her father to disappear like this.
example.tran: 就这样消失不像她父亲的一贯作风。
